  "texts": [
    "Upon visual examination, it is observed that the M-DQN model typically purchases Bitcoins at lower prices and sells them after the Bitcoin price significantly increases.",
    "This behavior demonstrates the effectiveness of the model in navigating the Bitcoin market.",
    "In this subsection, we present the experimental results of evaluating the performance of the proposed reward function by comparing it with two other reward functions in the literature.",
    "The objective of this comparison is to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed reward function in the context of Bitcoin trading, thereby highlighting its advantages over alternatives.",
    "The reward functions proposed by Allen et al."
  ]
